imdb.plot outline: The search for Ireland's next style star. 10 aspiring stylists, designers and fashion buyers battle it out a senior creative role with Aurora Fashions and a design contract with ByCaprice lingerie. Tasks ranged from window dressing to personal styling, advertorials to catwalk shows, photo shoots to dress design. Part advertiser-funded, sponsors included Bulmers Light, Special K, Lipton Tea, Scotch Hall Shopping Centre, Arnotts and the Daily Mail's You Magazine.
